	* Makefile: use setup.py to install
	* Merge branch 'makefile-use-setup-py' into next
	* Added 'build/' and 'MANIFEST' to cleaned files
	* Handle gracefully failure in privilege dropping
	* Added a comment about PyPy compatibility.
	* main/module.py: changed the way neubot dinamically loads a module's main() at runtime
	* Merge branch 'next.evfire' into next
	* Merge branch 'next'
	* main/__init__.py: no newlines in version pls
	* debian: return package version to -1
	* Release neubot/0.4-rc1

