	* http.handlers: Better protection vs. comet-after-close
	* http.clients: Make sure usage string is easier to understand
	* statusicon: Rewritten using httplib and threading
	* statusicon: Initial implementation of the popup menu
	* statusicon: Ubuntu has deprecated status-icon usage
	* notify: Increase interval between each check for pending events
	* main: Add a new speedtest command that invokes speedtest.main()
	* neubot: Make sure we employ safe_seek() in new code
	* Release neubot/0.2.4

